item.title: Building a Website as a Personal Artifact
item.description: There are lots of reasons why I have not built a personal webiste - the whole desgner problem of never being able to finalize a design, the lack of need, and my serial interest in trying new tools and learning them to a point but not putting that knowledge into practice. It will remain to be seen if this time is any different but I have a good feeling it is.
